msgid ""
"Firstly, we preprocess texts into tokens, as tokenizing a concatenated "
"string may produce different tokens than concatenating the results of "
"tokenizing each string individually. For example, assume we have a system"
" prompt and three text chunks. We need to preprocess them into tokens "
"before sending to the LLM:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/kv_cache_optimizations/blending.rst:59
msgid ""
"Then, we can send the tokenized prompt to vLLM. Meanwhile, LMCache will "
"store the KV caches of different chunks according to the "
"``BLEND_SPECIAL_STR``."
msgstr ""

